headlines.description: — Donovan Mitchell scored 22 points, Rudy Gobert had 17 points and 21 rebounds and the Utah Jazz extended their winning streak to six games with a 118-96 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mitchell, Gobert lead Jazz over 76ers for 6th straight win

events.name: Los Angeles Lakers at Memphis Grizzlies

headlines.description: — Jaren Jackson Jr. scored 25 points, Desmond Bane added 23 and the Memphis Grizzlies pulled away in the fourth quarter for a 108-95 victory over the Los Angeles Lakers on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Grizzlies ride second-half push to 108-95 win over Lakers

events.name: Denver Nuggets at San Antonio Spurs

headlines.description: — Derrick White had 23 points, Lonnie Walker IV added 21 and the San Antonio Spurs never trailed in beating the Denver Nuggets 123-111 on Thursday night, snapping a two-game skid.
headlines.shortLinkText: Spurs topple Nuggets 123-111, snapping two-game skid
